Profit and Loss (P&L) Statement Automation
Create an ETL pipeline that consolidates revenue and expense data to generate a P&L statement.

Understanding of revenue, cost of goods sold (COGS), gross profit, operating expenses, and net profit.

Data Extraction: https://catalog.data.gov/dataset/
revenue and expense data to set up P&L in the gas/banking industry

Data Transformation: pandas (Python), Power Query (Excel).

Cloud storage: AWS, Azure, or Google BigQuery.
Data Analysis:

Python (pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Seaborn).
R (ggplot2, dplyr).
